msgid ""
"When you hit a fiend or an undead with this magic weapon, that creature "
"takes an extra 2d6 radiant damage. If the target has 25 hit points or fewer "
"after taking this damage, it must succeed on a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw or "
"be destroyed. On a successful save, the creature becomes frightened of you "
"until the end of your next turn.    \n"
"While you hold this weapon, it sheds bright light in a 20-foot radius and "
"dim light for an additional 20 feet. \n"
